    <fix NullValue="1" type="string"/>
    <cause NullValue="1" type="string"/>
    <reference type="string">&lt;p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"&gt;To tell whether a list is an Outlook PDL (Public Distribution List), look up the owner information in the Outlook Address Book:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		From Outlook, click&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Address Book&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;or enter&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Ctrl+Shift+B&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		Enter the name of the&amp;nbsp;distribution list and double-click it.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		If the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Owner&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;field contains a person's name, the list is an Outlook PDL. If the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Owner&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;field says "Directory Works Managed," you will need to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://directoryworks.core.hp.com/" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 125, 186); text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" target="_blank"&gt;log into DirectoryWorks&lt;/a&gt;, search for the list in the top right corner, and contact the owners in order to have members added or removed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"&gt;Only PDL editors can add or remove members of an Outlook PDL. The owner of a PDL is often the editor, but not always. Editors can add or remove members using either Outlook or ATM (Automated Technology Manager).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px;"&gt;
	&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;IMPORTANT: If your Outlook has migrated to Office 365 Exchange Online&amp;nbsp;and you&amp;nbsp;are a PDL owner,&amp;nbsp;you can only edit PDLs using ATM. Please follow the steps below to edit members using ATM.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px;"&gt;
	&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;To edit members using Outlook:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		From Outlook, click&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Address Book&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;or enter&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Ctrl+Shift+B&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		Look up the PDL and double-click it.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		Click&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Modify Members&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		To add members:
		&lt;ol style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
				Click&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Add&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
				Type the name of the new PDL member (can be either a person or another Outlook PDL). When found, click&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Add&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
				Repeat step 2 until all new members are added.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
				Click&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;OK&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ol&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		To remove members:
		&lt;ol style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
				Click the first member to remove.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
				Hold the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Ctrl&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;key down and click any additional members to remove.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
				Click&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Remove&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
				Click&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;OK&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;until done.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
				Close the Address Book.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ol&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px;"&gt;
	&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;To edit members using ATM (Automated Technology Manager):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"&gt;NOTE:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;If your Outlook has migrated to Office 365 Exchange Online and you are a PDL owner, please&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"&gt;use ATM to manager PDLs&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		Log into&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="http://atm.corp.hp.com/redirect.asp?goto=SearchService&amp;amp;ServiceID=1025" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 125, 186); text-decoration: none; background: transparent;" target="_self"&gt;ATM&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		Scroll down to the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Exchange PDLs&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;section to see the PDLs for which you are the owner or editor.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		Click&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Options&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;next to the PDL you want to change.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		Click&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Select&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;next to the action you want to take (i.e.&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Add PDL Member&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;or&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;Remove PDL Member&lt;/strong&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		Follow the instructions to add or remove a member.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style="box-sizing: border-box;"&gt;
		Close your web browser to exit ATM.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"&gt;If you have issues accessing ATM, please follow&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://myitsupport.hp.com/myITsupport/ITSArticle?ArticleNumber=000002232" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 125, 186); text-decoration: none; font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;" target="_self"&gt;these steps&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: HPSimplified, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</reference>
